Finally we define some of our own convenience functions.

> decrease    a x = a -=  x
> increase    a x = a +=  x
> initialize  a x = a %=  (\case Nothing -> Just x; y -> y)
> prepend     a x = a %=  (x :)
> 
> oneOf  xs x = elem x xs
